column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, t.dr7objid, p.petrorad_r, p.petromag_r-p.extinction_r as petromag_r_dered, p.fracdev_r, p.modelmag_r-p.extinction_r as modelmag_r_dered, p.devrad_r, p.devab_r FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN PhotoObjDR7 t ON p.objID = t.dr8objid ORDER by x.up
